history.proof: intros A B a b l H. induction l as [|x l IHl]. -- simpl in H. contradiction. -- simpl in H. destruct H as [H | H]. ++ inversion H. subst. simpl. left. reflexivity. ++ simpl. right. apply IHl. auto.
